Package: python-automationhat
Architecture: all
Section: python
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python-rpi.gpio, python-sn3218
Suggests: python-psutil
Description: python library designed to control Automation HAT
 Automation HAT is a home monitoring and automation controller
 featuring relays, analog channels, powered outputs, and buffered
 inputs (all 24V tolerant).
 .
 This is the Python 2 version of the package.

